{"tid":1400598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦機場大罷工 最少170個航班被預先取消","createTime":"2019-08-03T13:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:05:06.000Z","uid":277446,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d650d5c3986aa7536089e0d97ca2ff3f2cb7d3","tid":1400598,"uid":277446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:25:27.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英國倫敦希斯洛機場（Heathrow Airport）是全英最繁忙機場，4000名員工日前臨時取消7月罷工，不過8月罷工行動將照常進行，目前下週一、二（5日、6日）共有177個航班被預先取消，預計影響約8.8萬名旅客。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，英國最大工會「聯合工會」（Unite The Union）表示，維安人員、消防員、工程師等約4000名會員投票否決資方修改後的薪資方案，其中又有88％支持罷工。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，罷工主因包括「同工不同酬」及「基層、高層薪資差異懸殊」問題。<br />\n<br />\n目前，希斯洛機場尚未詳細公布被取消的航班資訊，本週末將持續和聯合工會進行談判，規劃應變方案。同時，機場方面也呼籲在罷工日起飛的乘客，至少提前2至3小時抵達機場，因為安檢時間可能會拉長。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2873141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2873141&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OX5V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=5c6bfb43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2873141&h=00089610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2873141</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英文source:<br />\n<br />\nBBC<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/business-49212984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-49212984&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OX5V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=1e6c6462\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-49212984&h=fb0b8311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/business-49212984</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Guradian <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2019/aug/03/heathrow-airport-talks-resume-to-avert-strike-action\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fuk-news%2F2019%2Faug%2F03%2Fheathrow-airport-talks-resume-to-avert-strike-action&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OX5V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=75200f40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2019/aug/03/heathrow-airport-talks-resume-to-avert-strike-action</a><br />\n<br />\nFinancial Times<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/09e76682-b571-11e9-bec9-fdcab53d6959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F09e76682-b571-11e9-bec9-fdcab53d6959&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OX5V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=fa418c45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/09e76682-b571-11e9-bec9-fdcab53d6959</a>"},{"pid":"f0c1ba898e9901fc60d3c780639bcb3ea88ad31f","tid":1400598,"uid":40932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:26:18.000Z","msg":"英國經濟衰十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4f9e5dc1c0dcc406a39afe1a239aa47b024c07","tid":1400598,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"工會既重要性 - bargaining power"},{"pid":"f356ec31700e3ec3f11dfc03f6bee890712d8032","tid":1400598,"uid":277446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:28:10.000Z","msg":"The Gu<span style=\"color: red;\">ar</span>dian <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c4771d2a2afcbd8527c2768c7871413c165a62","tid":1400598,"uid":79655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"真罷工！"},{"pid":"614f519b9982ce5b8672e2f252e47c79fe136531","tid":1400598,"uid":277446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8d93cd664e5afd8813ec000505f0ceef39c062","tid":1400598,"uid":277446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:22:24.000Z","msg"